        {
            "title": "新世界發展連續第二年錄得虧損 因負債和樓市疲軟持續承壓",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"新世界發展連續第二年錄得虧損 因負債和樓市疲軟持續承壓\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FIULcDiB2EvwEyabDjrONw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-09/0cbca850-885a-11f0-b5f2-de38693d2242\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">新世界發展連續第二年錄得虧損 因負債和樓市疲軟持續承壓</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
